ibis.ipl.impl

Class WriteMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ibis.ipl.impl.WriteMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ibis.ipl.WriteMessage

    public class WriteMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements ibis.ipl.WriteMessage
    Implementation of the WriteMessage interface. This is a complete implementation, but may be extended by an implementation. In that case, the SendPort.createWriteMessage() method must also be redefined.
